      <title>What a gift to witness this mural come to life. 💛 I was so happy to have my moth...</title>
      <link>https://www.instagram.com/p/DVEp_ODkrps/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[<p><a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/DVEp_ODkrps/"><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/635014432_18035254877780882_2239954779597830707_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=104&amp;ig_cache_key=MzgzODM3NzQ0Njc1MjgyODAxMjE4MDM1MjU0ODcxNzgwODgy.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjM2MHg2NDAuc2RyLkMzIn0%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=UlUBs0dwHyMQ7kNvwHZAIOa&amp;_nc_oc=Adq1cNEOZ95lBZWV15WH0Ikng0Y7jXcfJ1ddfqXlBUI53l10wyiCxSUAJdMJhfqeL2M&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=EFwvYlGzAu_Ryp00L7AyBg&amp;_nc_ss=7a3ba&amp;oh=00_Afz4W3zmnXaeIgs-hwxHILx89Wo-wpJBSlMXoth9hBsOcw&amp;oe=69CA1446" alt="Video-thumbnail fra @katyyeaw" /></a></p><p><strong>🎬 Video</strong></p><p><strong>@katyyeaw</strong></p><p>What a gift to witness this mural come to life. 💛 I was so happy to have my mother, Esther Belinsky there by my side. <br/>
<br/>
Thank you Vista Hill Foundation, Elizabeth Tobias, Katy Yeaw, Angela Rowe, and Rachel Peniche for pouring your hearts into this beautiful space at the ParentCare Center. What an incredible way to honor Molly and Molly’s Angels.<br/>
<br/>
This room is more than paint on a wall — it’s hope, healing, and restoration for the women and families who walk through these doors. Vista Hill continues to do extraordinary work serving San Diego’s community in need of behavioral and mental health support, and I’m so grateful to stand alongside them.<br/>
<br/>
Together, we can create real change.<br/>
Together, we will keep loving it forward. 💫<br/>
<br/>
#MollysAngels #VistaHill #LovingItForward #MentalHealthMatters #SanDiegoCommunity</p><p><a href="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/o1/v/t16/f2/m69/AQMIFFs9_3wuyf6UAV_ax4cbeMEeMEsSO366ZG6psaB2EYU4PSO8eJBg7wsILZWlww31PBMm7HbC5SR0bL0TYtCO.mp4?strext=1&amp;_nc_cat=101&amp;_nc_sid=5e9851&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_ohc=NjWFEE6OTTwQ7kNvwEhnTq0&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6Inhwdl9wcm9ncmVzc2l2ZS5JTlNUQUdSQU0uQ0xJUFMuQzMuNzIwLmRhc2hfYmFzZWxpbmVfMV92MSIsInhwdl9hc3NldF9pZCI6MTc5NDUwMjA2OTUxMDY0MjQsImFzc2V0X2FnZV9kYXlzIjozMSwidmlfdXNlY2FzZV9pZCI6MTAwOTksImR1cmF0aW9uX3MiOjEzNSwidXJsZ2VuX3NvdXJjZSI6Ind3dyJ9&amp;ccb=17-1&amp;vs=5cec37b0c23e701&amp;_nc_&amp;_nc_gid=EFwvYlGzAu_Ryp00L7AyBg&amp;_nc_zt=28&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfwLHwFQPEskBrAbsExMOCI5otl7-h6NwhoNZDKocpPrQw&amp;oe=69CA3BFF">▶️ Åbn video direkte</a> · <a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/DVEp_ODkrps/">se på Instagram</a></p>]]></description>
